snippet.title: Thedas Calls - Dragon Age Day (2023) - Dragon Age: Dreadwolf
snippet.description:
Dragon Age: Dreadwolf™ full reveal summer 2024.
 
Enter Thedas, a vibrant land of rugged wilderness, treacherous labyrinths, and glittering cities – steeped in savage combat and secret magics. Now, its fate teeters on a knife's edge.
 
Add Dragon Age: Dreadwolf™ to your Wishlist on your favorite platform to stay up to date.

Related links:
Learn more: https://www.ea.com/games/dragon-age
